            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Libero Patri <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Albinius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ouf</abbr><ex>entina</ex></expan> Optatus <lb n="4"/>IIvir <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>man</abbr><ex>data</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> cum con<lb break="no" n="6"/>iuge liberis nur<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">is</supplied> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>nepot<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>b</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar senkrecht in zwei Hälften zerbrochen. (B): Passerini, AE 1947: Z. 3: Ou(fentina); Passerini, AE 1947: Z. 7: n[uru], in AE 1947 als Z. 6. nur[is?] offenbar nachträglich in kleineren Buchstaben zwischen die letzte und ursprünglich vorletzte Zeile gemeißelt.</p>
            </div>
